{
  "stem": "26111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was also-- our train, by the way, was met-- was, was, was combined at [GERMAN], at the, at the border-- with a train from Vienna that brought Viennese children.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were less than when we-- maybe half or less, even-- a third, maybe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we arrived there as a mixed Berlin-Vienna bag-- we arrived in England.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'd never met a Viennese before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there were, there were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You mean, like, counselors or something like-- there were, there were grownups around, yes, there were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were all English.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a rabbi, I'm sure, and, you know, one, one-- sure.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes, one could-- yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I should, I should amend that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I should amend that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The reason, probably, why I don't remember is that-- I don't remember that aspect of things-- is because I was 14.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think that the main demand for services of these comforting people would come from the younger ones-- would come from the ones who really didn't understand, didn't-- to the same extent that we older ones already did.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was one reason, in fact, why we didn't want to take up the time of the people-- of the rabbi and all these-- because they had their hands full with the ones that really needed it, which was the younger ones.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And were there any--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had some, some role in that, as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we-- somewhat, you know, took a little, somewhat, care of the younger ones, as far as we could.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we weren't-- some were more used to it than others-- those with large families that had taken care of young, young siblings, were better at it than others.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I can remember, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until March of '39.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Three months, about.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
